flowchart LR
    subgraph Client
        A[User Browser]
        B[React Frontend (Vite)]
        A --> B
    end

    subgraph API[ClipTalk Backend (FastAPI)]
        C[Routing & Middleware\n(CORS, Sessions, Logging)]
        D[Auth & User Services]
        E[Movies & TV Services]
        F[Social Features\n(Reviews, Comments, Watchlist, History, Recommendations)]
        B -->|HTTPS /api/*| C
        C --> D
        C --> E
        C --> F
    end

    subgraph DataLayer[Data & Caching]
        G[(PostgreSQL\nUsers, Movies/TV, Reviews, Comments, Watchlist, History, Preferences)]
        H[(Redis\nCache + JWT Blacklist + User Cache)]
    end

    D --> G
    E --> G
    F --> G

    D --> H
    E --> H
    F --> H

    subgraph External[External Services]
        I[TMDb API\nMovie/TV Metadata]
        J[External Ratings APIs]
        K[OAuth Providers\n(Google, Facebook)]
    end

    E <-->|Async HTTP (httpx)| I
    E <-->|Async HTTP (httpx)| J
    D <-->|OAuth Flows| K
